Anne Gwynne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Gwynne 0 Anne Gwynne (born Marguerite Gwynne Trice; December 10, 1918 – March 31, 2003) was an American actress and model who was known as one of the first scream queens because of her numerous appearances in horror films. Gwynne was also one of the most popular pin-ups of World War II. She is actor Chris Pine's grandmother.
